{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 11986, "create_time": 1640018921, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 1, "text": "[tmp]\n嗯？", "timestamp": 1640018921}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 11990, "create_time": 1640018973, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "桃花石人的劣根性", "timestamp": 1640018973}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 11992, "create_time": 1640019070, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\n桃花石本身不特别，就像托勒密埃及一样不特别，像印加帝国一样不特别。真正特别的是在爱琴海沿岸诞生的人类文明，文明人将像战胜所有βάρβαροι那样消灭桃花石在世上的存在。", "timestamp": 1640019070}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 11997, "create_time": 1640019107, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\n去找我的“今日历史神学”。", "timestamp": 1640019107}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12003, "create_time": 1640019258, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Carol: 所以，你的意识形态的核心就是西方中心主义?", "timestamp": 1640019258}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12004, "create_time": 1640019283, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "不过如此，见得多了", "timestamp": 1640019283}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12006, "create_time": 1640019397, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\n如果说生物的存在是为了让人类出现，那么人类的存在就是为了让文明出现，没有文明的人类与其余动物没有两样，文明就是人类的意义所在。必须用一切方法确保文明的长存，这就是我所有言论的核心。", "timestamp": 1640019397}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12007, "create_time": 1640019443, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 经度是一个循环坐标，没有什么“西方”这一说，有的只是文明。", "timestamp": 1640019443}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12010, "create_time": 1640019629, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 希腊与埃及的经度相差无几，托勒密王朝的僭主们也操着和希腊人一样的语言，但这并不妨碍一者是文明的，一者是野蛮的。", "timestamp": 1640019629}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12023, "create_time": 1640020408, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 小屁孩，小时候是不是屁股的打少挨了，所以现在这么叛逆", "timestamp": 1640020408}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12026, "create_time": 1640020716, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 6, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 桃花石人总是会试图将一切纳入到他们对世界特有的认知中，例如在他们眼中，用肉体的痛苦“教训”自己的后代是再正常不过的事，毕竟他们不过是困难时期的储备粮，而一切“异常”大抵都是由不依循桃花石的伟大传统所致。当然，文明，哪怕是文明的表象，对桃花石人都算得上是”异常”。", "timestamp": 1640020716}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12028, "create_time": 1640020752, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 没听说过真正有教养的文明人天天以污蔑诋毁为能事", "timestamp": 1640020752}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12037, "create_time": 1640020987, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 文明人天天说核弹? 如果这就是所谓文明精神的话，那这几百年西方还真是发扬光大了文明精神，贩卖黑奴，杀人越货，无恶不做，确实应该是你的精神归属地", "timestamp": 1640020987}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12040, "create_time": 1640021057, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "我不能再和这么无聊的人说了", "timestamp": 1640021057}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12068, "create_time": 1640022691, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "看了一圈下来反而觉得Dave水平不是很高", "timestamp": 1640022691}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12072, "create_time": 1640022844, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Grace: 不论道理如何，开始看格调、逼格这些了是吧😅", "timestamp": 1640022844}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12146, "create_time": 1640049940, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "我格调不高，水平不行，一套一套话不会说，但我骂一句天火哥傻逼玩意，这么粗浅的道理没啥问题吧", "timestamp": 1640049940}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12250, "create_time": 1640057028, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 为什么文明人不能使用天火这文明最伟大的结晶呢？难道文明人不曾尝试过和平地改变桃花石人吗？难道为了拯救桃花石的婴儿来到桃花石的“神圣童年协会”没有被桃花石人屠杀吗？", "timestamp": 1640057028}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12253, "create_time": 1640057319, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 所有人口达到一定数量的群体都会发展出奴隶制，然而文明人是唯一自发地要废除奴隶制的。黑奴在美洲作奴隶的生活，比在黑非洲作奴隶的生活好上无数倍，之所以现在文明人痛恨自己曾奴役黑人的历史，无非是因为他们是文明的，而没有直接向黑人传播文明。人们对“大西洋奴隶贸易”耳熟能详，却对持续时间长得多，奴隶生活残酷得多的“印度洋奴隶贸易”一无所知，也正是这个道理。", "timestamp": 1640057319}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12256, "create_time": 1640057714, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Isabella: 沙特是一个独裁宗教国家，为什么美国不颠覆沙特呢", "timestamp": 1640057714}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12260, "create_time": 1640057918, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: 我从未说过文明人不会犯错误。", "timestamp": 1640057918}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12261, "create_time": 1640057934, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 嘴上都是主义，脑子里都是生意", "timestamp": 1640057934}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12262, "create_time": 1640057950, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Isabella: 为什么犯错至今不承认不改正呢", "timestamp": 1640057950}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12264, "create_time": 1640058039, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Bob: 希特勒之前的德国不能不说是个文明国家吧，欧洲思想精神高地", "timestamp": 1640058039}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12265, "create_time": 1640058054, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: “至今”才有多少时间？文明人犯下最大的错误，就是在韩战中否决了麦克阿瑟天才的作战计划，但这并不影响文明人仍是文明的。", "timestamp": 1640058054}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12266, "create_time": 1640058082, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: 神圣罗马帝国是“思想精神高地”？", "timestamp": 1640058082}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12268, "create_time": 1640058183, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: 普鲁士是“思想精神高地”？", "timestamp": 1640058183}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12272, "create_time": 1640058521, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "十九世纪德国浪漫主义发源地，盛产哲学家音乐家物理学家", "timestamp": 1640058521}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12330, "create_time": 1640060005, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Isabella: “所有人口达到一定数量的群体都会发展出奴隶制，然而文明人是唯一自发地要废除奴隶制的。黑奴在美洲作奴隶的生活，比在黑非洲作奴隶的生活好上无数倍，之所以现在文明人痛恨自己曾奴役黑人的历史，无非是因为他们是文明的，而没有直接向黑人传播文明。人们对“大西洋奴隶贸易”耳熟能详，却对持续时间长得多，奴隶生活残酷得多的“印度洋奴隶贸易”一无所知，也正是这个道理。”\n你看看你这是人的逻辑吗？不稀得跟你说", "timestamp": 1640060005}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12335, "create_time": 1640060170, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "文明人犯错、奴役黑人、杀人越货、贩卖鸦片、屠戮印度人，是可以理解的，是好的。是吧", "timestamp": 1640060170}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12353, "create_time": 1640061203, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: 十九世纪的德意志诸国当然可以算作文明世界的一部分，但肯定算不上“高地”。希特勒的统治来自墨索里尼的统治，墨索里尼的统治来自布尔什维克的统治，布尔什维克的统治直接继承俄罗斯帝国，而俄罗斯帝国当然源于蒙古人的统治，蒙古人的统治来自于哪里当然是众所周知的。", "timestamp": 1640061203}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12354, "create_time": 1640061242, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 如果文明人没有与黑非洲接触，黑奴会被黑奴隶主奴役到今天。", "timestamp": 1640061242}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12359, "create_time": 1640061295, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 文明人如今忏悔，是因为他们“本可以做得更好”，而野蛮人则根本没有“做”的可能性。", "timestamp": 1640061295}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12366, "create_time": 1640061612, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "德意志是日耳曼人，和你的希腊圣源根本不是一个族类，这也可以算作文明人里吗？照你这么说什么都可以算作文明人里面，只要这个民族之后经济上发展起来，让你足够羡慕。按你这说法，恐怕日本人也应当是“天生的”文明人，之后又什么野蛮国家经济文化崛起了，你也会改口说这本来就是“文明人”。", "timestamp": 1640061612}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12371, "create_time": 1640061735, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Jason: 他们确实可以做得更好，他们应该把印度进一步压榨，让所有人都被敲骨吸髓，他们还应该进一步奴役中国人，再洗劫远超过圆明园和故宫的财宝", "timestamp": 1640061735}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12373, "create_time": 1640061869, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "逆民我们前几年见多了，不算新鲜，都是不懂历史，自卑而眼馋，没有自己的灵魂罢了", "timestamp": 1640061869}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12379, "create_time": 1640062096, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你所说的文明世界里，百分之一的人拥有百分之九十九的财富，文化教育只是这少部分人才享受得起的，而这少部分人却同时以支配无产者的妻女为乐，并以相互诱奸妻子为乐，和你设想的文明风气差远了。剩下的大部分人，文化资本并没有多少，很多仅仅能费力维持生存，和你见到的所谓野蛮国家的大多数劳动者过得一样苦，一样“不文明”。", "timestamp": 1640062096}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12383, "create_time": 1640062216, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你这思想意识，放在所谓文明社会里 都会被右派指为极右、法西斯，那些文明社会也容不下你", "timestamp": 1640062216}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12385, "create_time": 1640062315, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你想给人家当奴隶恐怕也费劲", "timestamp": 1640062315}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12387, "create_time": 1640062450, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 我什么时候提到“族类”的事了？", "timestamp": 1640062450}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12388, "create_time": 1640062547, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: “支配妻女”，桃花石人的想象力也就这样了，毕竟“妻女”在桃花石都是财产，而桃花石的僭主都会抢夺走桃花石人的财产，因此文明世界也就应当是如此的。", "timestamp": 1640062547}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12389, "create_time": 1640062587, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Jason: 那日耳曼人算不算文明人（虽然他们的文明史可能不过两千年）", "timestamp": 1640062587}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12390, "create_time": 1640062648, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Jason: 是，应当如此，首先就要应验到你身上", "timestamp": 1640062648}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12391, "create_time": 1640062679, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: “一样，一样”，桃花石人眼中的世界是同质的，因为他们无法理解与他们不同的人类，桃花石人创造出了“易子而食”的成语，那么文明人想必也有这样的表达吧。", "timestamp": 1640062679}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12394, "create_time": 1640062754, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 什么日耳曼人？文明与否与种族无关，托勒密王朝的僭主们都来自希腊，这不妨碍他们是纯粹的野蛮人。", "timestamp": 1640062754}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12396, "create_time": 1640062862, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你还真是朽木不可雕也，逻辑不同，有什么好再说的呢", "timestamp": 1640062862}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12397, "create_time": 1640062875, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 11, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 桃花石人的潜意识里，谈到“人”时就必然指的是男性，而“妻女”当然只不过是财产和储备粮。", "timestamp": 1640062875}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12399, "create_time": 1640062895, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Jason: 那日本人算不算文明人", "timestamp": 1640062895}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12401, "create_time": 1640062926, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 现在的日本人，作为一个整体，是文明人。", "timestamp": 1640062926}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12403, "create_time": 1640062991, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "如果托勒密王朝的人做了和日耳曼人一样的事，他们还是不是野蛮人?", "timestamp": 1640062991}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12409, "create_time": 1640063302, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "作为文明人的日耳曼人怎么追随希特勒了。希特勒也不过是人心欲望的一个唤醒者", "timestamp": 1640063302}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12410, "create_time": 1640063383, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Jason: 你知道文明世界里也有奴隶和奴隶主，奴隶在奴隶主的监管下做工，不仅要养活自己还要养活奴隶主，之后靠奴隶主给他的少于自己做工成果的仅够自己家里生活的配额去领取本是奴隶制造的生活消费品吗？你知道这文明社会里，奴隶曾经在十八世纪十九世纪时每天要工作十二个小时吗？你知道长期的过度劳动和营养不良睡眠不足让他们身体羸弱，甚至种族退化吗？", "timestamp": 1640063383}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12413, "create_time": 1640063504, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 和哪些日耳曼人一样的事？", "timestamp": 1640063504}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12414, "create_time": 1640063531, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 你知道桃花石人“易子而食”吗？", "timestamp": 1640063531}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12416, "create_time": 1640063573, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你根本不知道，你只能看见文明社会里的奴隶主们穿着板正的西装打着领带喝红酒，或者穿上运动服带上太阳帽去打高尔夫球，让你感觉十分眼馋。\n你就是个财迷心窍，没有自我意识，人格卑下的逐利蛆虫罢了", "timestamp": 1640063573}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12418, "create_time": 1640063582, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 10, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 你知道《愤怒的葡萄》曾在桃花石因为“美化”文明世界而被禁吗？", "timestamp": 1640063582}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12421, "create_time": 1640063757, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "我有我不知道的，你也有你不知道的，都谦虚些，多方面全面了解了再说，再申明主张用核弹否", "timestamp": 1640063757}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12423, "create_time": 1640063787, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: 一部分文明可能陷落于野蛮，正如从亚历山大帝国到托勒密埃及，从罗马共和国到罗马帝国那样，但文明本身必须长存，必将长存。", "timestamp": 1640063787}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12424, "create_time": 1640063849, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Jason: 愤怒的葡萄被禁，是这个野蛮国家本来野蛮。我回答了。\n那你该回答我说的文明世界里的这些野蛮行径是为什么了", "timestamp": 1640063849}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12428, "create_time": 1640063877, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 你大可以比较一下维多利亚时期的一个普通英国工人与同时期一个普通桃花石农民的日均摄入热量，看看到底谁是“奴隶”。", "timestamp": 1640063877}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12429, "create_time": 1640063969, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "我来替你说把，你的文明世界其实也是充满着肮脏的东西的野蛮世界的外表粉饰所现罢了", "timestamp": 1640063969}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12431, "create_time": 1640064091, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "如果文明自身从野蛮中脱胎，他有责任度化野蛮，度化野蛮的最有效方式就是像他过去得到的那样，给野蛮以财富。\n文明承认错误也要弥补错误，从东方掠夺的就应该等价还给东方，从非洲掠夺的就应该等价还给非洲", "timestamp": 1640064091}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12432, "create_time": 1640064111, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 什么野蛮行径？文明正是要消灭一切野蛮行径，而只有在此过程中尚未被消灭的才会被人记住。你会记住美洲的黑奴，却不会记住黑非洲的黑奴，会记住英属印度下的一场饥荒，却不会记住此前无数次死亡人数多得多的饥荒，因为后者只是平常，而前者却是文明世界的一次失败。", "timestamp": 1640064111}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12434, "create_time": 1640064165, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "开始比烂了? 我没说野蛮世界是文明的。照你说的，野蛮世界本该野蛮，你文明世界为什么也如此野蛮呢？", "timestamp": 1640064165}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12435, "create_time": 1640064250, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Louis: 你可以去看看资本论，里面有对十八十九世纪的纺织工人、爱尔兰人的悲惨生活、种族退化的叙述。", "timestamp": 1640064250}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12437, "create_time": 1640064326, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你说说的文明世界也不过是充满了野蛮罢了", "timestamp": 1640064326}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12439, "create_time": 1640064341, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: 你所在的这座学校，不就是文明世界“还”的吗？文明世界为桃花石付出的太多了，天花疫苗拯救了十万百万桃花石人，传教士们拯救了本会死在“义塔”里的婴儿，但桃花石人当然更愿意崇拜屠杀者。", "timestamp": 1640064341}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12440, "create_time": 1640064360, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "乌鸦笑猪一般黑", "timestamp": 1640064360}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12441, "create_time": 1640064480, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 爱尔兰人的悲惨生活缔造出了爱尔兰共和国，而桃花石人受再多苦难也只会将过去的事一再重复。文明不是乌托邦，而是人类前进的动力和方向。", "timestamp": 1640064480}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12442, "create_time": 1640064492, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "而你所谓的野蛮国家却没有到你的文明国家去贩卖鸦片、贩卖文明国家的人口、屠杀文明国家的人。\n如果你说贩毒、贩卖人口、屠杀本来就是文明国家的特权，那好吧，确实是", "timestamp": 1640064492}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12444, "create_time": 1640064601, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Louis: 爱尔兰人的共和贵不是他们一味当奴隶，贩卖自己的人口，让民族的个体埋在火车轨道下面就可以做到的，而是他们反抗斗争所得。你丝毫不懂历史", "timestamp": 1640064601}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12448, "create_time": 1640064720, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 13, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 仅仅是因为βάρβαροι做不到罢了，但他们当然会屠杀——真正的屠杀，而不是文明人在镇压拳乱时做的那样——没有进入文明的ξένοι，比如桃花石对柬埔寨“输出革命”。", "timestamp": 1640064720}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12449, "create_time": 1640064739, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "“你所在的这座学校，不就是文明世界“还”的吗？”\n用抢来的钱的一部分还给他们，让他们派人来我们这里，把这些他们国家的精英也培养成我们的精神奴才，我们可以更加长久地奴役这个国家。\n这就是文明的算盘", "timestamp": 1640064739}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12450, "create_time": 1640064807, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 13, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 为了人类的福祉而反抗斗争不就是只在文明世界才存在的吗？我昨天才分享了一首IRA（爱尔兰共和军）的歌，不知道从哪里看出我“不懂历史”。", "timestamp": 1640064807}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12451, "create_time": 1640064818, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "而且建国后，清华就不是老清华了，之后的清华是直接靠人民的钱建的，不像之前是间接的", "timestamp": 1640064818}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12453, "create_time": 1640064896, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Margaret: 读史明理，明因果先后，你记个歌算啥，你读再多东西，没有知道历史逻辑就是看了个狗屁", "timestamp": 1640064896}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12454, "create_time": 1640064935, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你不会是反串吧，这些本来有什么难想的呢？", "timestamp": 1640064935}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12457, "create_time": 1640065017, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你的那个鬼希腊文可别显摆了吧，不就是一种拼音吗？换成拉丁字母又有什么区别呢", "timestamp": 1640065017}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12459, "create_time": 1640065228, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你别说别的，也别比烂，只要解释为什么你的文明世界中从古至今充满这么多野蛮行径，甚至野蛮是它经济制度的底层动力。你只要解释这个", "timestamp": 1640065228}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12465, "create_time": 1640065423, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你这种人，前几年见得可多了，我从来不屑一顾，现在想着他们大多数大概有点脑子和自尊了吧，没想到还有个你是原地踏步。", "timestamp": 1640065423}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12466, "create_time": 1640065433, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你这种人，前几年见得可多了，我从来不屑一顾，现在想着他们大多数大概有点脑子和自尊了吧，没想到还有个你是原地踏步。", "timestamp": 1640065433}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12468, "create_time": 1640065438, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 文明人为了在拳乱中被桃花石人杀死的被教堂保护的人（其中绝大多数都是桃花石人）而以赔款惩罚桃花石的僭主，但桃花石人当然更愿意与鼓励他们互相残杀的僭主共情。", "timestamp": 1640065438}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12471, "create_time": 1640065529, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "对你说人话没用，你只配在每次说话时得到恰如其分的SB两个字", "timestamp": 1640065529}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12472, "create_time": 1640065619, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你倒不如多学点科学的东西，这才是文明世界如果可以说是文明的原因。别学历史和人文了，你吃不了这碗饭", "timestamp": 1640065619}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12474, "create_time": 1640065627, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 14, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 到底什么叫野蛮行径？如果让工人加班是“野蛮行径”，那么“易子而食”算什么？人吃人是最公认的野蛮行径，那么究竟什么地方“充满”字面意义的人吃人？你自己说“一样，一样”，怎么又怪我将文明世界与桃花石做比较？", "timestamp": 1640065627}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12476, "create_time": 1640065717, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 14, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Dave: 你怎么知道我学的专业是什么呢？我所掌握关于人类历史的一切，都不会超过一个普通文明人所知。", "timestamp": 1640065717}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12482, "create_time": 1640065995, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "你只在脸皮厚上是无敌的", "timestamp": 1640065995}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12691, "create_time": 1640074505, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 15, "text": "一切皆是野蛮，宇宙从原人的献祭与肢解中来，又复归于人的身体。普罗米修斯从天上窃取天火，这是人类苦难之始；普罗米修斯在分肉时偷梁换柱，由此开启了人类短寿的命运。一切从火中来，一切到炙烤牺牲的浓烟中去。", "timestamp": 1640074505}], "create_time": 1640018768, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1640074505, "likenum": 13, "n_attentions": 13, "n_comments": 88, "pid": 4291, "poll": null, "reply": 88, "text": "有没有人能用大白话总结一下天火哥整天神神叨叨的究竟要表达些啥，仅仅就是想说桃花石很垃圾？", "timestamp": 1640018768}}